---

## Run It Locally

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/retail-banking-budget-simulator.git
cd retail-banking-budget-simulator
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
```

App will open at `http://localhost:8501`

---

## About This Project

Built as a finance analyst portfolio project to demonstrate annual budget cycle and long-range planning skills relevant to retail banking finance roles. The model is calibrated against publicly available banking industry benchmarks and Federal Reserve economic data to ensure the simulated outputs reflect realistic planning scenarios.

